      • StudyGroup

        public StudyGroup()
        Default constructor uses for csv parser. Don't use it to create objects.

      • StudyGroup

        public StudyGroup(long id,
                  String name,
                  Coordinates coordinates,
                  Long studentsCount,
                  int expelledStudents,
                  long transferredStudents,
                  FormOfEducation formOfEducation,
                  Person groupAdmin)
           throws IllegalArgumentException
        Constructor with parameters. Use it to create objects.
        Parameters:
        id - Group's id. Must be unique and greater than 0.
        name - Group's name. Name can't be null or empty.
        coordinates - Group's coordinates. Can't be null.
        studentsCount - Count of students in group. Count be greater than 0 and can't be null.
        expelledStudents - Count of expelled students in group. Count should be greater than 0.
        transferredStudents - Count of transferred students in group. Count should be greater than 0.
        formOfEducation - Group's form of education. Form of education can't be null.
        groupAdmin - Group's admin. Can be null.
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - If any parameter is wrong.
        See Also:
        Coordinates, FormOfEducation, Person
